caption: Jack and Jack are literally an inspiration and I'm so glad they are my idol. I'm so happy that they met and started making videos when they were younger that soon progressed to this. All of their music is amazing and you get a deeper meaning listening to every lyric. I don't think they understand how much they mean to us and no one can compare to them. I'm excited for when we hear them everyday of the radio and then they will have fans calling in to try to win tickets to sold out concerts. The events will be much much larger and all we will look back at how we were here since day one and they are still living their dreams. We love you so much #contest #contest #contest #contest
